{"tid":2452709,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港台：中美開場發言激烈交鋒　雙方互相指責違反禮節","createTime":"2021-03-19T04:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T04:35:04.000Z","uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd58ea48ed044ea718eaf15c53706422aba80e7e","tid":2452709,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"中美高層官員在阿拉斯加會談開場發言時激烈交鋒，<strong>中方代表團官員事後指責美方，在先致開場白時嚴重超時，並對中國內外政策無理攻擊指責，挑起爭端，認為這樣不是待客之道，也不符合外交禮儀，中方對此作出嚴正回應。</strong><br />\n<br />\n這名官員又說，<strong>中方帶著誠意，應邀到安克雷奇同美方進行戰略對話，並做好按雙方事先商定的程序和安排開展對話的準備。</strong><br />\n<br />\n而美國一名高層官員就說，中方代表似乎有意譁眾取寵，公開作秀，違反禮節。這名官員說，雙方在會談前同意，開場發言只有兩分鐘，但最後變成超過一小時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581451-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581451-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSq%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=e072107d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581451-20210319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=43d711eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581451-20210319.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"492cb55dcff1551edabb639638fd0ded58d5baca","tid":2452709,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"睇黎蘋果既報導中和下先<br />\n<br />\n美聯社：楊潔篪超時發言令布林肯「吃了一驚」<br />\n美聯社形容，<strong>布林肯聽見楊潔篪言論的篇幅之長、姿態之高後「看來吃了一驚」</strong>，他其後回應楊潔篪時，坦言過往與各國領導人交流時，以至日前訪問日本及南韓期間，從各國所得的印象皆與中國截然不同。布林肯表示，他從各國口中聽見「美國回來了，我們重新投入國際事務」，亦透露其他國家同樣深切關注中國政府的所作所為。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院在聲明中批評中方代表在開場發言時，違反兩分鐘發言時間上限，質疑有人譁眾取寵，只顧「演戲」而不顧事實。美國國務院強調美方在對華交流有信心，亦相信美國可變得更完美。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210319/UIKCEHG74FGKPLAVHFTI2UBCSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FUIKCEHG74FGKPLAVHFTI2UBCSY%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSq%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=8002fb1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FUIKCEHG74FGKPLAVHFTI2UBCSY%2F&h=faf65b5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210319/UIKCEHG74FGKPLAVHFTI2UBCSY/</a>"},{"pid":"48f83327459d25156f1b585080784998a4fdb4fa","tid":2452709,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:13:10.000Z","msg":"做一輪戲先.再閉門互含??"},{"pid":"b81f82c2a034258f41175299d6d53b1ceff2f9de","tid":2452709,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"打未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06833d59d9660ac411c8169db64ae66f08bd67e","tid":2452709,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f83327459d25156f1b585080784998a4fdb4fa","tid":2452709,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:13:10.000Z","msg":"做一輪戲先.再閉門互含??"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"郭文貴都係咁講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2452665/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2452665/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"cd384c4230aa74c759ba6b1eabcdad9b61158863","tid":2452709,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a06833d59d9660ac411c8169db64ae66f08bd67e","tid":2452709,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48f83327459d25156f1b585080784998a4fdb4fa","tid":2452709,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:13:10.000Z","msg":"做一輪戲先.再閉門互含??"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"郭文貴都係咁講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2452665/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2452665/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"吊,原來條友仲未自殺死"}]}